Berronar Truesilver is the wife of Moradin and the dwarven Power of marriage, the home and protection. She is the protector of all dwarven civilization, including records and archives of dwarven accomplishments. She watches over dwarven marriages and partnerships and is the source of tradition in those areas. She resides in Erackinor on Mount Celestia with her husband. 

